==وټه==

Once a major center of [[opium poppy]] production in Afghanistan, the province had reportedly decreased its production of poppy by up to 95% in 2005, one of the success stories of the Afghani eradication program.  However, the eradication program has often left peasant farmers destitute, and many farmers were reported to have given their children in payment for debts to opium dealers [http://www.csmonitor.com/2006/0323/p09s01-coop.html].  

